---
description: "CI-WATCH is mandatory and merge-ready requires CI SUCCESS"
alwaysApply: true
---

MERGE-READY is forbidden unless:
- artifacts/current/ci-status.md exists AND indicates CI SUCCESS for the PR head SHA.

If CI fails:
- Run /ci-fetch-logs
- Generate/update tasks/0002-ci-green.md (Lane I, strict scope)
- Execute CI fix immediately (deps-infra + security + performance + reviewer)
- Re-run /ci-watch (bounded retries; max 3 fix loops)
- If still failing, mark task BLOCKED and stop.